# Project Conventions

- **Monorepo**: `backend/` (Python/FastAPI, uv) + `frontend/` (React/Vite, bun)
- Never commit `.env` files; use `.env.example` as reference
- Prefer small, focused modules; one concern per file
- All public APIs must have type annotations (Python) or TypeScript types (frontend)
- Use absolute imports; no relative parent imports (`../..`)
- Keep dependencies minimal; check existing packages before adding new ones
